      "guaranteed_return",
      "validated_alpha",
      "inevitable_price_movement"
    ]
  },
  "known_limitations": [
    "U1/U2 did not confirm stable total_score ranking power.",
    "Historical universe, listing, ST, and suspension states can be current-snapshot-limited.",
    "Industry, fundamental, event, policy, and versioned historical status data are not reliably available.",
    "Static lists overlap and are research views, not independent production portfolios.",
